                    <span>Just know this book has you developing code in the SDK, not Visual Studio .NET.  If anything that should turn you away from buying this.  
<br />
<br />Any .NET programmer WILL be working with Visual Studio and not an SDK.  
<br />
<br />The SAMS teach yourself C# in 24 hours was completely written for VS .NET, so I am confused as to why this book was not.
<br />
<br />Get another book as this one will be only of use for terminology and OOP theory.  It was a waste on Money for me.
<br /></span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">There are better books to start with.</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
